@page "/contact"

<PageTitle>联系方式 | 天门龙</PageTitle>

<section class="section-block">
    <div class="section-heading">
        <h1>把客户最关心的沟通入口先放出来</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-grid">
        <article class="contact-card">
            <h3>合作咨询</h3>
            <div class="contact-line">
                <span class="contact-label">微信</span>
                <span class="contact-value">your-wechat-id</span>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-line">
                <span class="contact-label">QQ</span>
                <span class="contact-value">your-qq-number</span>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-line">
                <span class="contact-label">邮箱</span>
                <span class="contact-value">your-email@example.com</span>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-line">
                <span class="contact-label">电话</span>
                <span class="contact-value">可在这里填写手机号或商务联系电话</span>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article class="contact-note">
            <h3>建议客户联系时说明</h3>
            <ul class="contact-list">
                <li>项目类型：App、桌面端、官网、上位机、管理系统等。</li>
                <li>目标平台：Android、iOS、鸿蒙、Windows、Linux、macOS。</li>
                <li>当前阶段：新项目、已有项目二开、原型验证、长期维护。</li>
                <li>时间要求：是否有明确上线时间或演示节点。</li>
            </ul>
        </article>
    </div>
</section>
